[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    329[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAWS CloudTrail and Amazon CloudWatch.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m CloudTrail data events on every PHI-bearing store and on case data stores. Every investigator action, every case state change, every data access is logged. CloudWatch dashboards for pipeline health and detector operating metrics. This audit trail is not optional; it's part of the regulatory posture of the program.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    330[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    331[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAWS Clean Rooms (optional, for multi-payer collaboration).[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Some schemes span payers (a provider billing Medicaid, Medicare Advantage, and commercial payers for the same patterns). Multi-payer intelligence sharing is regulated but permitted in specified scenarios. AWS Clean Rooms enables privacy-preserving joins across multiple payer datasets. Not a day-one feature, but worth knowing about.[K
